Sovereign AI Hardware Virtualization (SAIHV)Project: Digital BIO Defense Protocol 
v2.2Executive SummaryIn 
an era of increasing dependency on centralized cloud AI, the SAIHV project establishes a framework for Architectural Sovereignty. This repository demonstrates a hardware-agnostic, self-governing kernel designed to decouple AI logic from static host environments. By moving away from hardcoded dependencies and implementing automated entropy management, this protocol ensures that an AI's "state" is as portable and resilient as the data it manages.Core Architectural Pillars1. Agnostic Seeker Logic (Environmental Awareness)Standard AI deployments are often "brittle"—linked to specific local paths. The SAIHV Kernel utilizes a Relative Handshake ($O(2n)$ search offset). Upon boot, it performs a forensic scan of its sibling directories to locate its data silo.Utility: Seamless migration between local workstations, NAS, and cloud-mirrored directories (Google Drive/OneDrive) without code modification.2. Binary Encapsulation & The Root of TrustTo prevent "Configuration Drift" and unauthorized logic tampering, the PowerShell source is compiled into a Sovereign EXE (C# wrapper).Stability: Ensures the kernel remains immutable during transit.Security: Establishes a hardened gateway between the host OS and the sensitive data sheets.3. Sovereign Vaulting (Persistence Model)The architecture implements a Binary Storage Tier:The Vault: A protected, immutable zone for core identity seeds and persistent IP.Transient Telemetry: A governed log directory for session metadata.4. Entropy Janitor (Automated Governance)To maintain high-speed cloud synchronization and prevent technical debt, the kernel features an integrated Automated Lifecycle Manager.Function: Automatically identifies and purges transient logs older than 14 days.Benefit: Keeps the "Digital Footprint" lean and prevents sync-bloat.Technical SpecificationsRuntime: PowerShell Core / .NET Compiled Binary.Targeting: X64 Hardware Virtualization.Sync Logic: Optimized for real-time cloud-mirroring integrity.Identity Logic: Hardened Digital BIO Defense naming conventions.
